29acd6111050004","tid":2205569,"uid":365024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fac8a3849d842442b44d202352b1c0e9eff73dc0","tid":2205569,"uid":226156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0d0714bbe97376630bb979755f38f1e6294fd3d","tid":2205569,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8cacaef6a0591e396e051309cbc2de703209393c","tid":2205569,"uid":226156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T03:09:26.000Z","msg":"如果係咁辯方更加要執住「張金福」呢條柒頭點解自行出現響警署門口呢個pt黎上訴。佢話返緊工所以行經果度，但事實果日警總咁大根本無人響正門返工，咁點解佢出現響果度，佢根本係刻意出現響現場破壞現場，佢根本有份導致暴動，姐係控方證人係講根大話，完全不可信<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T03:13:42.000Z","msg":"佢好似自辯中伏認咗非法集結"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T03:20:39.000Z","msg":"非法集結同暴動本身係2個concept，唔可以混為一談"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T03:35:57.000Z","msg":"如果一個非法集結commits a breach of the peace, 個集結就係暴動"},{"pid":"cf04041c16bf9ba1c41178a95f167a75c87267d0","tid":2205569,"uid":199739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T04:02:06.000Z","msg":"#區域法院第廿八庭<br />\n#郭啟安法官 #裁決<br />\n👤岑(25) #0626警總<br />\n‼️還押逾9個月‼️<br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n(1) 暴動<br />\n(2) 襲擊他人致造成身體傷害<br />\n(3) 不依法庭指定歸押 (已認罪)<br />\n<br />\n控罪(1)罪名成立🤦&zwj;♂️<br />\n控罪(2)罪名不成立，交替控罪普通襲擊罪名成立<br />\n<br />\n已承認控罪(3)<br />\n<br />\n🛑休庭至11:00等待辯方準備求情<br />\n<br />\n--------------------------<br />\n郭官不會在庭上宣讀裁決理由<br />\n<br />\n🛑司法機構官網已上載裁決理由<br />\n重點證據分析，由第61段開始<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://legalref.judiciary.hk/lrs/common/ju/ju_frame.jsp?DIS=130847&amp;currpage=T\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flegalref.judiciary.hk%2Flrs%2Fcommon%2Fju%2Fju_frame.jsp%3FDIS%3D130847%26currpage%3DT&d=WBhgCLuhUD%2FUeH80S3I9%2BpFDRn80AWZfiUxX1c6OkmY%3D&h=db31e830\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://legalref.judiciary.hk/lrs/common/ju/ju_frame.jsp?DIS=130847&amp;currpage=T</a><br />\n<br />\n基於法庭在「暴動」罪所作為分析及裁決，被告人在本案發生時在灣仔警署外是刻意向控方第一證人施以非法武力（即兩拳和一腳），故意或罔顧地使控方第一證人受到非法武力的侵犯。<br />\n<br />\n辯方提出，被告人雖然承認有以武力對付控方第一證人，但是他在出第一拳時是出於自衛。整體而言，他也是因為見控方第一證人推跌一名女士令她倒地受傷，他是為了防止罪案發生而使用武力去嘗試制服控方第一證人或阻止他繼續攻擊其他示威者。<br />\n<br />\n基於以上分析 (判案書第102至105段)，法庭不接納被告人在施襲時合理地相信他正受襲或防止罪案發生；法庭亦不接納他真誠地如此相信<br />\n<br />\n本席認為控方亦可以因為被告人非法使用武力而證明他是知道或罔顧襲擊控方第一證人的行為，特別是在群情洶湧的情況下，是相當可能導致任何人合理有「訂明的害怕」<br />\n<br />\n🛑<br />\n無論被告人是否參與了較早前夏慤道暴動的延續，抑或他是獨立地作出攻擊而致使他身處的非法集結也即時演變成暴動，任何一種情況也完全乎合公安條例第19條的元素。無論從任何一個角度，被告人都是干犯了「暴動」罪。"},{"pid":"234ec828f0c6847931f14ca38215828975b4cfc3","tid":2205569,"uid":181172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0003f2107e5e90e91fe52b100ae0dfc745bbd871","tid":2205569,"uid":8014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c48d3cf2b5339522d3a3174603df3258d1f42599","tid":2205569,"uid":304431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7abc7c484aaae9ffd38abadbc0262aa734f47b3f","tid":2205569,"uid":8014,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T02:39:53.000Z","msg":"算把啦你<br />\n你除左嬲之外做到咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家咪又係番緊工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有撐黃店已經好好"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T02:59:58.000Z","msg":"好過你放負先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T03:09:30.000Z","msg":"黃衛兵痴鳩線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n明明同路人撐黃店撐蘋果 又唔柒得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想點撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T04:04:00.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6023eae8c409e192b98dd1ad7d733847f90a45b5","tid":2205569,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67521324a61c6b6d862f9002237da5173b50eeee","tid":2205569,"uid":8014,"like":10,"dislike":91,"score":-81,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T02:22:41.000Z","msg":"手足唔係condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今晚食黃店買蘋果 撐手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T04:05:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"70d9f2ff41333eb771509c8f497af07ad8a6626e","tid":2205569,"uid":199739,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T02:32:37.000Z","msg":"🛑司法機構官網已上載裁決理由<br />\n重點證據分析，由第61段開始<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://legalref.judiciary.hk/doc/judg/word/vetted/other/ch/2019/DCCC000825_2019.docx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flegalref.judiciary.hk%2Fdoc%2Fjudg%2Fword%2Fvetted%2Fother%2Fch%2F2019%2FDCCC000825_2019.docx&d=WBhgCLuhUD%2FUeH80S3I9%2BpFDRn80AWZfiUxX1c6OkmY%3D&h=bc727124\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://legalref.judiciary.hk/doc/judg/word/vetted/other/ch/2019/DCCC000825_2019.docx</a><br />\n<br />\n當被告人見控方第一證人正在逃跑，其他示威者從後追打，期間在轉身時他將該名女士撞倒，法庭必須重申認為這並不是一件獨立事件。在當時的大環境加上現場的氣氛下，有示威者無故被人推撞等同是有敵對的人將與他們相同理念的「支持者」襲擊<br />\n<br />\n法庭因此並不接納辯方陳詞所指被告人對控方第一證人的施襲是個別、獨立或偶然的行為。相反，法庭認為辯方的說法是以偏概全，不設實際。"}}